<li class="c12 c2" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; padding-left: 0pt; margin-left: 36pt; direction: ltr;">麻省理工学院MIT(<span class="c4" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline;"><a class="c10" href="http://mirrors.mit.edu/" style="text-decoration: inherit;">http://mirrors.mit.edu/</a></span>)</li>
<li class="c12 c2" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; padding-left: 0pt; margin-left: 36pt; direction: ltr;">哥伦比亚大学(<span class="c4" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline;"><a class="c10" href="http://mirror.cc.columbia.edu/" style="text-decoration: inherit;">http://mirror.cc.columbia.edu/</a></span>)</li>
<li class="c12 c2" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; padding-left: 0pt; margin-left: 36pt; direction: ltr;">俄勒冈州立大学(<span class="c4" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline;"><a class="c10" href="http://ftp.osuosl.org/pub" style="text-decoration: inherit;">http://ftp.osuosl.org/pub</a></span>)</li>
