<li class="c12 c2" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; padding-left: 0pt; margin-left: 36pt; direction: ltr;">杜克大学(<span class="c4" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline;"><a class="c10" href="http://archive.linux.duke.edu/" style="text-decoration: inherit;">http://archive.linux.duke.edu/</a></span>)</li>
